quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  7,79,"Then he [Sâlih] turned from them, and said: "
  7,80,"And (remember) Lût (Lot), when he said to his people: "
  7,81,""
  8,13,"This is because they defied and disobeyed Allâh and His Messenger. And whoever defies and disobeys Allâh and His Messenger, then verily, Allâh is Severe in punishment."
  8,14,"This is (the torment), so taste it; and surely for the disbelievers is the torment of the Fire."
  8,15,"O you who believe! When you meet those who disbelieve, in a battle-field, never turn your backs to them."